Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:14.93,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:15.49,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:18.91,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:22.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:26.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:30.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:34.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:36.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.78,0:00:40.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:45.05,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.05,0:00:48.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:51.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:54.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:59.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:03.09,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:11.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:13.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:15.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.31,0:01:18.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.85,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,210.389)}My Name is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.85,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,690.389)}Monster Bird Gillgaras!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.67,0:01:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the deadman gas\Nexperiment ready to proceed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.10,0:01:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.69,0:01:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The deadman gas takes effect\Nin five seconds, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... siphon out the gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Any human exposed\Nto the deadman gas
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.55,0:02:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to thirst\Ninsatiably for human blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use the deadman gas to force\Nnot just the people of Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but all the people of Japan\Nto hate and kill each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Assign the newly-created\Ncyborg Gillgaras to the task
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.91,0:02:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and initiate the\Nslaughter of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.16,0:02:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider! Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That crow is so smart.\NIt even talks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cool how it knows\Nhow to say "Kamen Rider."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, I want this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I want this crow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:03:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What a creepy crow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But you promised\Nto buy me anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.11,0:03:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to take care of\Nit, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How much is the crow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider! Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please! Crows can't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This one can.\NWhat do you want me to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, there.\N- Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going\Nto see the crow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The crow's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.31,0:03:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshiko in the Agatsuki\NApartments bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wow, weird taste, huh?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.17,0:03:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But that crow could even sing about\NKamen Rider and Shocker and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think crows\Ncan talk like people?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- Crows?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Crows caw and cats meow,\Nand that's how it's always been.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm gonna check!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Crows caw and cats meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.27,0:04:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I thought\Nyou were fearless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're as human\Nas the rest of us, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're hanging out together,\Nthere must not be much going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.98,0:04:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's been keeping\Na low profile lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It means we can do\Na lot of training.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's perfect\Ntiming, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro's been acting strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked me a question\Nabout talking crows,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:05:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and then he wandered\Noff, mumbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking crows?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Since you're such\Na good friend, Goro,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll lend you my\Ncrow for one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come by my room, okay?\N- Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She just insisted, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it back this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.12,0:05:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Crows have always\Nmeant bad fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we at least wait\Nuntil she gets home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just looking at\Nit creeps me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And all this talk of crows talking\Nlike people... it's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm taking it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker! Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?\NIt's very unsettling...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Eiko... look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A crow monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Foolish humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hate each other!\NFight each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Send each other to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the deadman\Ngas has taken effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, kill each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Just wait here, okay?\N- Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Yoshiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My Mom and Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency! Someone come help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They're... They're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all the hubbub?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like they killed each\Nother out of pure hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone in the complex is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they all tore\Neach other apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one entity in the world\Nthat could do something so awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What an awful thing to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.85,0:07:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Goro.\NWe can't stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She's fainted from the shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:40.45,Italics,,0,0,0,,Enemies of Shocker,\NIchimonji Hayato and Taki Kazuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,This will make the\Nperfect prison for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:47.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,Now, receive my\Nbaptism of deadman gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...\NShocker knew we would come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji, the gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, boost me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji! You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more than human.\NI'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker cyborg...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the one behind this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All humans exposed to the deadman\Ngas will tear each other apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I call it Operation:\NHuman Annihilation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That certainly sounds like the\Nwork of an evil Shocker assassin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But sorry to say,\NI'm putting an end to your plot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Try it, if you can, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can and I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel numb! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The gas is taking effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like it's\Nworking, Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The deadman gas turns\Nhumans into killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But it does one more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The deadman gas has a\Nspecial side effect...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When used against a\Ncyborg, it paralyzes them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hayato!\N- Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato,\Nthe Kamen Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,has been hospitalized\Nfor full-body paralysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our chance to be rid\Nof Shocker's greatest enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Our scientists report that injecting\Nthe Kamen Rider with Gamma G,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:11:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the core material\Nof the deadman gas,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,will completely destroy him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let us administer\NGamma G to the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Gillgaras!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:22.70,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Which should I pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so hard to choose...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.71,0:11:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, if you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.85,0:11:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A crow, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a unique crow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, go and sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.44,0:11:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider! Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sold!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider! Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems fast asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we wake him up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. We'll get a\Nscolding from the Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But we carried this heavy\Nthing all this way to see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's asleep,\Nmaybe we should just leave it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hush. Save it for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait until Hayato's\Nawake to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as you're told,\Nor we'll fry you up and eat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.47,0:12:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do people really eat fried crow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinshu Ueda is famous\Nfor crow dengaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All three of you together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how's Mr. Ichimonji doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't regained\Nconsciousness since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A crow? There's an\Nunusual bedside present.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:13:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just any crow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NIt can talk like humans do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the crow that\NGoro was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't act so scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a man selling birds...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Selling birds? Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.62,0:13:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I get for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A crow.\NAnd one that talks, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.98,0:13:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows that\Ncrows can't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're claiming ignorance?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.67,0:13:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tease me, please, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop playing dumb.\NI know what's going on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.66,0:13:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You just sold it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you sell that crow\Nas a present for Ichimonji?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.34,0:13:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,To purge this world\Nof Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!\NIt's too late to stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,By now, Gillgaras will have\Nput an end to the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the great Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is left paralyzed and bedridden\Nby the power of the deadman gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I'll put him\Nout of his misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gamma G will destroy him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is not\Nthe only Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Hongo Takeshi...\Nthe first Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:14:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Hongo Takeshi, the one who's\Nbeen undermining Shocker's Europe Branch?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.91,0:15:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato sent me a message\Njust before he lost consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll still make\Na worthy opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, breathe my deadman gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He was all talk after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick Hongo Takeshi\Ninto the gas chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.44,0:16:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We've produced\Nenough deadman gas
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to turn everyone in Tokyo\Ninto a mindless murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now initiate the plan,\Nfocusing on the Keihin Industrial Belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:36.57,Italics,,0,0,0,,Emergency in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:38.89,Italics,,0,0,0,,There is a deadman\Ngas leak in Z-Block.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You... but you breathed\Nin the deadman gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There was an antidote in one\Nof the European Shocker bases.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.65,0:16:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I used it to save both\NIchimonji Hayato and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Death... surrender already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.63,0:17:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence, fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Gillgaras!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Gillgaras!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.11,0:17:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We may have lost this base,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but the poison gas\Nwe've stored up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,still has the power to drive all of the\Npeople of Tokyo to madness and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:17:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.94,0:18:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Gillgaras has a\Ntanker of the gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll disperse the\Npoison from the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let it happen, Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.69,0:18:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chairman, Tokyo's in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.63,0:18:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to try\Nto stop Gillgaras.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:18:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's show the people of Tokyo\Nthe power of this poison gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Gillgaras!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.55,0:19:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast, Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the tanker and\Nrelease the gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.99,0:21:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.98,0:22:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Double Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.73,0:22:18.52,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\3c&H9F9E86&\c&H2E27C0&}Tokyo International Airport
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a new\Nmission ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo...\NI won't let you outshine me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can expect to see\Namazing things from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.30,0:22:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's South America\NBranch is formidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be just fine.\NYou worry about Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.68,0:22:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only one I have,\Nbut to remember me by...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.49,0:22:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.10,0:22:59.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato would leave Japan\Nto fight Shocker in South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.63,0:23:03.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the first Kamen\NRider, Hongo Takeshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.29,0:23:06.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,would be back in\Naction in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:10.51,Cont,,0,60,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.86,0:23:13.03,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.86,0:23:14.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:16.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Jaguar Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:18.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With razor-sharp claws\Nand incredible speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.19,0:23:20.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he stops Kamen\NRider in his tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.28,0:23:23.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Jaguar's roar sends a\Npeaceful zoo into chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.29,0:23:25.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:28.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "The Monstrous Jaguar Man's\NDeadly Motorbike Battle."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:30.86,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(467.167,710.389)}The Monstrous Jaguar Man's\NDeadly Motorbike Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.64,0:23:40.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:43.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.06,0:23:45.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:48.07,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.57,0:23:50.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.44,0:23:52.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.32,0:23:54.11,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.11,0:23:55.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.95,0:23:57.95,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.00,0:24:03.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.72,0:24:07.25,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.25,0:24:10.85,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.33,0:24:14.99,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My Name is Monster\NBird Gillgaras!